        "body": "Yes, definitely true. \r\n\r\nThe previous implementation was much cleaner and we had to write much less code. \r\nThe carousel Example:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\r\n  <div class=\"item\">\r\n    <img src=\"./1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"item active\">\r\n    <img src=\"./2.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"item\">\r\n    <img src=\"./3.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n```",
